{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c88737ddba","title":"对班禅额尔德尼祝贺新年电报的复电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2ddb16d9e5","index":0,"year":1956,"month":1,"day":21,"articleId":"c88737ddba"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"5f8b98c8aa","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c88737ddba","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"班禅额尔德尼，即班禅额尔德尼·确吉坚赞，西藏宗教领袖之一，当时任政协全国委员会副主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c16b19a2d3","type":"title","text":"对班禅额尔德尼祝贺新年电报的复电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c88737ddba"},{"id":"5f8b98c8aa","type":"paragraph","text":"班禅额尔德尼","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c88737ddba"},{"id":"4177f776f5","type":"paragraph","text":"谢谢你的新年祝贺。过去一年内，日喀则地区的经济文化建设工作有进步，我们听到了都很高兴。现在由于全国人民的努力奋斗，我们的国家一年比一年繁荣兴旺，西藏地方和别的地方一样，都是要一年比一年兴旺起来的。在新的一年内，你们那里也将会有更大的进步。我祝你身体健康，学业精进，希望你在新的一年内为进一步加强民族团结，实现民族区域自治，做出重大的贡献。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c88737ddba"},{"id":"e1808876dd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c88737ddba"},{"id":"74550df5a9","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年一月廿一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c88737ddba"}],"page":{"id":"6fda9434c0","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c88737ddba","start":176,"end":176}}}},"__N_SSG":true}